So, you want to create your own game. That's great. 
To show you how you can do this with Little Goblin, this section will explain how the
reference implementation (the demo game) works and giving you hints where and 
how to start your own development.
 
h2. Prerequisites

You should know a little bit of Grails. "The Grails website":http://www.grails.org/learn is your friend.

It will also help to have some general programming knowledge.